      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PROWL (4) proved too good on debut over 520m at this track to score by 1.5 lengths (30.09). Can make it back to back wins. Can continue winning ways. HELLO ELSA (1) stalked the pace then proved too strong in the run home to record her maiden win (30.01) at this track over 520m. Drawn well off an inside draw. Harder here but expected to measure up. TYANA BURN (3) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten 1.5 lengths (30.19) behind PROWL at this track. Expected to feature. CLEAN AIR (2) was in the money two back in a Maiden at this track then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when third (30.25) over 520m at this track.",
